{"tid":395990,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"何謂港獨？","createTime":"2017-09-11T10:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T17:26:22.000Z","uid":24362,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1c13e5b26aaf35f700abd8996a385e2939fbefe4","tid":395990,"uid":24362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:20:22.000Z","msg":"其實港獨係唔係口號黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟港獨實際上係點樣執行<br />\n從軍事上政治上抑或經濟上？<br />\n係兩登聽左港獨兩個字幾年仍然唔明白咩叫港獨<br />\n當我發夢夢到港獨成功啦<br />\n咁究竟成功港獨既香港係點樣呢？<br />\n利申：唔係想挑連登仔機，純粹賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc66ca5320fac82776fdbaa205ad1ec14bcb5f1","tid":395990,"uid":24362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"開錯係吹水台"},{"pid":"df7294a2bb318c4ff69cd3b40dab3ede1cc32848","tid":395990,"uid":24362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38eb784d963bdc0668f378ebf58f18564ae966f4","tid":395990,"uid":24362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:16:45.000Z","msg":"係咪冇人答到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aafce4ad46f18afbfa995947c85f63db15827e6","tid":395990,"uid":45368,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:34:12.000Z","msg":"應該無人答到你<br />\n依家個個都淨係為左嘈嬴場交<br />\n下一步都無人諗<br />\n你講到咁遠出邊d人會以為你唔支持佢地<br />\n<br />\n我係第二個post問呢d 問題就比人鬧我失敗主義、小朋友、五毛<br />\n樓主都自己小心啦"},{"pid":"dce82368e4016be1efaee2c7eb3c280b5a1e3df7","tid":395990,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁究竟成功港獨既香港係點樣呢？</blockquote><br />\n間間茶餐廳部部電視機都唔再系長開播住TVB"},{"pid":"f04cc8008fcfae000a1ca241a298676844acad2f","tid":395990,"uid":24140,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"直到不再受支那迫害"},{"pid":"789